name: Wave Function Collapse (Demo)
description:
This is a small project that uses wave function collapse to generate a small map. It's purpose is only to visually exemplify the procedural generation of a map using the algorithm, but you are free to use it however you please. 

You use the demo in the browser, or you can download the project files from the project's repository: https://github.com/cyborg-kenneth/wave-function-collapse
